<h2>Itching or burning, Puffy eyelids and Watery eyes</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms itching or burning, puffy eyelids and watery eyes including Hay fever, Allergic reaction, and Indoor allergens.</p>
<p>There  are 14 conditions  associated with itching or burning, puffy eyelids and watery eyes. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
